# Codeowners file for security approvals

# Security team owns all security-related files
.github/workflows/security-ci.yml @security-team
SECURITY.md @security-team
.pre-commit-config.yaml @security-team
.github/dependabot.yml @security-team

# Core team owns main code
*.py @core-team
tools/ @core-team
main.py @core-team

# DevOps team owns CI/CD
.github/workflows/ @devops-team
Dockerfile @devops-team

# Default: maintainers own everything
* @maintainers